<h3 id="research-work">Research Work</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Trigger Optimization Framework in Salesforce</strong> – A comprehensive architectural framework that has been devised to optimize trigger execution in Force.com Platform. This architecture has been designed to increase performance, enhance scalability and bring forth developer-less configurations to control trigger execution in the Cloud.</li>
</ul>

